---
title: Cal Smart Harissa Barramundi with Roasted Veggie Couscous
description: This light meal, featuring succulent barramundi, is made unforgettable thanks to flavour inspiration from North African cuisine. For a wholesome twist, we swapped out classic breadcrumbs for spicy hummus sauce.

Calorie Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie amount.
